  "name": "Rat Snake Swarm",
  "pfs": {
    "availability": "Standard",
    "subtype": "pfs",
    "type": "stat_block_section"
  },
  "schema_version": 1.4,
  "sections": [
    {
      "name": "Rat Snake Swarm",
      "sections": [
        {
          "image": {
            "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png",
            "name": "Additional Lore",
            "type": "image"
          },
          "name": "Slithering Packs",
          "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
          "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
          "sources": [
            {
              "link": {
                "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
                "aonid": 276,
                "game-obj": "Sources",
                "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Monster Core 2",
              "page": 294,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "subtype": "sidebar",
          "text": "Despite their solitary natures, snakes come together in swarms for purposes of hibernation or mating. However, a few species have learned to stick together and coordinate their hunting efforts, leading to slithering packs of predatory snakes.",
          "type": "section"
        }
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
            "aonid": 276,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core 2",
          "page": 294,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "A solitary snake might be no cause for alarm, but a hissing mass of frenzied snakes can make even seasoned adventurers shudder. Rat snakes can reach lengths of up to 10 feet, and they gather en masse to hibernate as well as to breed. Though nonvenomous, these territorial snakes will strike anything that threatens them.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
    {
      "link": {
        "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
        "aonid": 276,
        "game-obj": "Sources",
        "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 294",
        "type": "link"
      },
      "name": "Monster Core 2",
      "page": 294,
      "type": "source"
    }
  ],
